314
00:22:59,590 --> 00:23:06,520
♫  Love is the food for the living heart  ♫

315
00:23:07,760 --> 00:23:09,560
♫  Love  ♫

316
00:23:15,460 --> 00:23:16,650
Hello, how are you?

317
00:23:16,650 --> 00:23:20,050
Hello. Are you Miss Lin Kesong?

318
00:23:20,050 --> 00:23:25,480
- Yes, I am.
- I am the President of Hyatt Restaurant. I am Xiao Hua.

319
00:23:25,480 --> 00:23:29,960
Hello. I think I've heard of your restaurant.

320
00:23:29,960 --> 00:23:34,680
- It's our honor. Our restaurant is opening our first branch in Shanghai.

321
00:23:34,680 --> 00:23:37,520
We are recruiting talents.

322
00:23:37,520 --> 00:23:39,290
We really hope that you will join us.

323
00:23:39,290 --> 00:23:41,090
Me?

324
00:23:41,800 --> 00:23:43,720
Aren't you looking for Mr. Jiang?

325
00:23:43,720 --> 00:23:46,000
It's because you are Mr. Jiang's apprentice.

326
00:23:46,000 --> 00:23:48,820
Also, in the Mueller's Future Star Culinary Competition,

327
00:23:48,820 --> 00:23:51,530
you have already entered the finals. Your strength is clearly visible.

328
00:23:51,530 --> 00:23:54,030
I have to thank you for your affirmation.

329
00:23:54,030 --> 00:23:58,940
But, my strength isn't as good as you think.

330
00:23:58,940 --> 00:24:02,300
If you aren't looking for Mr. Jiang, I'll hang up now.

331
00:24:02,300 --> 00:24:06,180
Then, you are thinking of going to Yuxuan?

332
00:24:06,180 --> 00:24:10,700
My goals is to learn culinary arts from Mr. Jiang.

333
00:24:10,700 --> 00:24:15,530
And then bring more delicious foods to people.

334
00:24:15,530 --> 00:24:17,860
Okay. Goodbye.

335
00:24:26,320 --> 00:24:29,840
Qianfan, how is it? Did you hear?

336
00:24:32,220 --> 00:24:34,060
I heard.

337
00:24:35,630 --> 00:24:37,120
She couldn't tell, did she?

338
00:24:37,120 --> 00:24:39,770
Don't worry. She didn't.

339
00:24:39,770 --> 00:24:43,120
That's it for now. Rest well.

340
00:24:52,930 --> 00:24:55,040
I'm back!

341
00:25:07,460 --> 00:25:09,790
What are you doing?

342
00:25:13,180 --> 00:25:15,720
I was just testing the oil temperature. Why are you so nervous?

343
00:25:15,720 --> 00:25:18,320
But you shouldn't test with your hand.

344
00:25:19,680 --> 00:25:22,350
I just don't want to keep waiting for death.

345
00:25:23,420 --> 00:25:25,490
Why are you so anxious?

346
00:25:25,490 --> 00:25:29,030
A lifetime is long. I'll just stay with you and test together, right?

347
00:25:35,810 --> 00:25:37,580
Lin Kesong.

348
00:25:40,720 --> 00:25:42,960
I'm sorry.

349
00:25:42,960 --> 00:25:45,420
Why sorry?

350
00:25:47,960 --> 00:25:50,490
Didn't you just get a phone call?

351
00:25:53,960 --> 00:25:56,330
I asked someone to call you.

352
00:26:04,490 --> 00:26:06,450
What do you mean?

353
00:26:07,620 --> 00:26:12,020
I just wanted to hear the truth from you. I tested you.

354
00:26:13,700 --> 00:26:16,120
Didn't I already tell you everything?

355
00:26:17,770 --> 00:26:19,920
Don't you trust me?

356
00:26:22,820 --> 00:26:25,390
Tell me, what else can I trust now?

357
00:26:25,390 --> 00:26:28,600
I'm useless now. I can only sit and wait for death.

358
00:26:28,600 --> 00:26:33,660
But you? You are growing up every day, getting more fierce every day.

359
00:26:33,660 --> 00:26:37,830
How do I know if you really want to stay with me, or maybe there's a motive?

360
00:26:40,490 --> 00:26:42,450
Jiang Qianfan.

361
00:26:45,390 --> 00:26:47,740
Are you done?

362
00:26:47,740 --> 00:26:50,520
Do you understand what love is?

363
00:26:51,930 --> 00:26:53,880
Love means, when I stay with you to eat sugar and chew vegetables,

364
00:26:53,880 --> 00:26:57,480
when I go to the mountain of blades and sea of flame, but I still feel happy.

365
00:26:57,480 --> 00:26:59,830
I trusted you so much.

366
00:27:01,860 --> 00:27:05,790
Until today, you'd actually get someone to test me in secret.

367
00:27:09,630 --> 00:27:11,730
You don't trust me?

368
00:27:12,460 --> 00:27:15,130
Okay, starting today,

369
00:27:15,130 --> 00:27:18,500
I won't intervene what you do. You can do whatever you want to do.

370
00:27:28,070 --> 00:27:29,890
Lin Kesong.

371
00:27:32,160 --> 00:27:34,060
Lin Kesong.

372
00:28:09,610 --> 00:28:11,280
Kesong.

373
00:28:23,720 --> 00:28:25,330
This way.

374
00:28:26,610 --> 00:28:28,170
Come.

375
00:28:36,660 --> 00:28:38,660
Sit over there.

376
00:28:51,310 --> 00:28:55,320
If everything turned out like what I imagined, how wonderful would it be?

377
00:28:56,180 --> 00:28:59,900
Too bad that reality isn't what I dreamed.

378
00:28:59,900 --> 00:29:03,800
The more beautiful the dream, the reality is so helpless.

379
00:29:03,800 --> 00:29:06,220
And you can't help but accept it.

380
00:29:06,220 --> 00:29:10,660
Luck, when will you knock on the door?

381
00:29:21,320 --> 00:29:22,990
What are you doing here?

382
00:29:22,990 --> 00:29:25,930
Hello, Miss Lin.

383
00:29:25,930 --> 00:29:27,620
I'm sorry that I'm bothering you.

384
00:29:27,620 --> 00:29:31,630
I'm looking for Mr. Jiang. I have some stuff for him.

385
00:29:31,630 --> 00:29:33,850
- We don't...
- Let him come in.

386
00:29:43,880 --> 00:29:46,900
You don't look much good this way.

387
00:29:50,160 --> 00:29:51,980
Are you satisfied?

388
00:29:57,580 --> 00:30:00,380
I brought you this.

389
00:30:07,410 --> 00:30:09,150
What is it?

390
00:30:10,640 --> 00:30:13,450
It's the last page in Montgomery's notebook.

391
00:30:17,250 --> 00:30:18,610
What do you mean?

392
00:30:18,610 --> 00:30:22,440
Please read the last sentence to you.

393
00:30:29,330 --> 00:30:30,280
[But, I am sugar.]

394
00:30:30,280 --> 00:30:34,280
But, I am sugar.

395
00:30:40,840 --> 00:30:43,300
[I hate sugar, but I'm sugar.]

396
00:30:47,430 --> 00:30:52,330
I hate sugar, but I am sugar.

397
00:30:53,330 --> 00:30:57,430
After Montgomery's accident, I received the notice

398
00:30:57,430 --> 00:31:01,030
and rushed to his home. None of you were there.

399
00:31:01,030 --> 00:31:05,040
You went to the seaside to wait for news on the rescue.

400
00:31:05,790 --> 00:31:10,730
The notebook was open, right on the counter.

401
00:31:10,730 --> 00:31:14,590
I guessed that Montgomery was making a dessert.

402
00:31:14,590 --> 00:31:17,800
He didn't have any inspiration, that's why he went out to the sea.

403
00:31:18,660 --> 00:31:24,000
To revenge against you, I tore off a piece and left.

404
00:31:24,760 --> 00:31:31,170
I know that you're very loyal, especially to Montgomery.

405
00:31:31,170 --> 00:31:34,790
If you knew, his last words to you were "I hate sugar",

406
00:31:34,790 --> 00:31:37,850
you definitely wouldn't touch sugar every again.

407
00:31:37,850 --> 00:31:42,320
In this way, not only would you be further away from happiness,

408
00:31:42,320 --> 00:31:45,440
you'd also be at a greater disadvantage.

409
00:31:46,360 --> 00:31:51,090
You'd never be able to reach the top with your cooking.

410
00:31:54,170 --> 00:31:58,700
Unfortunately, I was only half right.

411
00:31:58,700 --> 00:32:03,000
You were indeed no longer happy.

412
00:32:03,000 --> 00:32:05,690
But your dishes

413
00:32:08,010 --> 00:32:10,220
stayed amazing.

414
00:32:16,860 --> 00:32:19,460
You chose to tell me this now

415
00:32:22,440 --> 00:32:25,490
because I'm no longer your opponent.

416
00:32:25,490 --> 00:32:27,570
Right?

417
00:32:27,570 --> 00:32:29,350
No.

418
00:32:30,490 --> 00:32:34,990
I decided to tell you this now

419
00:32:34,990 --> 00:32:38,160
because I only just came to understand

420
00:32:39,600 --> 00:32:41,690
that I was wrong.

421
00:32:42,660 --> 00:32:45,800
I tried everything I could to strike you down.

422
00:32:46,510 --> 00:32:48,730
But as a result,

423
00:32:51,340 --> 00:32:53,660
I ended up being even more miserable than you.

424
00:32:54,800 --> 00:32:59,010
If I keep living like this,

425
00:32:59,010 --> 00:33:01,920
my life would be meaningless.

426
00:33:04,420 --> 00:33:07,800
I'm sorry, Qianfan.

427
00:33:17,290 --> 00:33:22,750
This is all the sugar I've collected from all over the world.

428
00:33:23,590 --> 00:33:25,390
I'm giving it to you.

429
00:33:26,890 --> 00:33:29,320
Teach Lin Kesong well.

430
00:33:31,610 --> 00:33:33,380
I should get going now.

431
00:33:34,120 --> 00:33:37,160
But can I say a few words

432
00:33:37,160 --> 00:33:40,150
to Jiang Qianfan before I go?

433
00:33:41,130 --> 00:33:43,920
Just say whatever it is you have to say with me here.

434
00:33:54,590 --> 00:33:56,820
Head to your room for now.

435
00:33:58,260 --> 00:33:59,940
Go inside.

436
00:34:15,120 --> 00:34:17,590
I'm leaving soon.

437
00:34:17,590 --> 00:34:22,030
I'm going to be a chef on a cruise.

438
00:34:22,650 --> 00:34:27,290
This cruise trip travels in the North Atlantic all year long.

439
00:34:27,290 --> 00:34:30,460
It's even closer to Montgomery.

440
00:34:30,460 --> 00:34:35,260
Do you still want to stay here in your current state?

441
00:34:36,390 --> 00:34:38,450
Why don't you come with me?

442
00:34:38,450 --> 00:34:42,100
Work as my assistant. I can arrange it for you.

443
00:34:44,940 --> 00:34:46,750
Call me

444
00:34:48,020 --> 00:34:50,060
when you've decided.

445
00:34:51,400 --> 00:34:54,800
Goodbye. Take care.

446
00:34:59,160 --> 00:35:00,920
Boris.

447
00:35:06,040 --> 00:35:07,970
I'll go with you.

448
00:35:12,410 --> 00:35:14,720
Perhaps this is a better choice

449
00:35:24,120 --> 00:35:27,000
for me.

450
00:36:14,740 --> 00:36:16,740
He left?

451
00:36:18,090 --> 00:36:19,740
Yes.

452
00:36:20,320 --> 00:36:22,570
Are you going to forgive him?

453
00:36:24,520 --> 00:36:26,780
I hate Boris,

454
00:36:29,130 --> 00:36:31,360
but I am Boris.

455
00:36:33,520 --> 00:36:38,990
I'll never be able to be at peace with myself if I don't forgive him.

456
00:36:52,500 --> 00:36:54,570
Thomas?

457
00:36:58,130 --> 00:37:00,570
Hello, Mr. Thomas.

458
00:37:05,880 --> 00:37:07,710
What is he saying?

459
00:37:11,750 --> 00:37:15,310
Mr. Thomas said that the committee has drafted two announcements.

460
00:37:15,310 --> 00:37:20,200
The first statement is "Jiang Qianfan has decided to withdraw from the finals due to his blindness."

461
00:37:20,200 --> 00:37:25,010
The second is, "despite losing his sight, Jiang Qianfan

462
00:37:27,260 --> 00:37:31,490
s decided to join the finals." He is asking you which one you'd choose.

463
00:37:36,380 --> 00:37:42,300
Why is he asking when he already knows the answer? Tell him to stop finding excuses to show sympathy to me.

464
00:37:46,220 --> 00:37:47,950
Thomas—

465
00:37:50,860 --> 00:37:52,770
Alright.

466
00:37:58,120 --> 00:38:02,360
How are you so smart? You guessed it.

467
00:38:03,830 --> 00:38:06,240
He told me to take good care of you.

468
00:38:11,700 --> 00:38:17,630
It's exactly the same. From Thomas' words to Jiang Qianfan's current expression,

469
00:38:17,630 --> 00:38:22,740
my imagination perfectly coincided with reality.

470
00:38:22,740 --> 00:38:25,720
I'm at a loss for words.

471
00:38:25,720 --> 00:38:28,850
Perhaps reality is not so helpless after all.

472
00:38:29,560 --> 00:38:34,980
If your wishes are strong and powerful enough, hope really will be there.

473
00:38:39,080 --> 00:38:43,510
[The Statement Regarding Competition Mentor, Mr. Jiang Qianfan]

474
00:38:53,520 --> 00:38:55,510
Mom, you're back.

475
00:38:55,510 --> 00:39:00,430
Thomas just released a statement that Jiang Qianfan is not only competing in the finals, but he's making dessert as well.

476
00:39:00,430 --> 00:39:03,250
Why does he suddenly not hate sugar anymore?

477
00:39:03,250 --> 00:39:06,910
I don't know. Perhaps he never really hated it in the first place.

478
00:39:06,910 --> 00:39:09,030
Go pour me a glass of water.

479
00:39:09,030 --> 00:39:11,830
Mom, did you drink?

480
00:39:11,830 --> 00:39:14,410
It's still daytime.

481
00:39:14,410 --> 00:39:17,550
Your troubles aren't worried about whether it's day or night.

482
00:39:17,550 --> 00:39:20,740
I'm going to get changed. I'll teach you to make dessert in a bit.

483
00:39:32,390 --> 00:39:37,030
When sugar and water reach a temperature of 160° C,

484
00:39:37,030 --> 00:39:40,120
we'll get the effect we want.

