00:40:49,710 --> 00:40:51,540
Got it?

490
00:40:51,540 --> 00:40:53,520
O-Of course.

491
00:40:53,520 --> 00:40:57,120
You know that I'm able to make things upon watching for the first time.

492
00:40:57,120 --> 00:40:59,160
What's on your mind?

